The paper deals with generating image captions, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The proposed approach involves the use of recurrent neural networks (RNNs) and LSTMs, which are common techniques in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the task of describing novel objects, which could be related to information retrieval (cs.IR).
